.
.
.
Ingredients:
Sirloin steak 
Worcestershire sauce
Avocado oil
Butter
Minced garlic
Seasonings of your choice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cut steak into cubes. Mix in a bowl with Worcestershire sauce, oil, & seasonings.
2. Air fry at 400F for 7 minutes.
3. In a bowl melt butter and garlic. Toss the finished steak in the bowl and enjoy!
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #steak #carnivore

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 can of chicken
1 large egg
1/2 cup shredded cheese
Seasonings of choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mash your chicken up in a bowl and mix with all ingredients. 
2. Shape into nuggets and air fry on parchment paper at 400F for 8-10 minutes flipping halfway through.
3. Let cool & enjoy!
.
.
Notes: You can also bake at 400F for 20 mins flipping halfway.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:

.
.
Ingredients:
2 slices of low carb bread 
Ham
Cheddar 
Egg
Butter
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cut the crust off of your bread and flatten.
2. Whisk your egg in a bowl. 
3. Add your ham and cheddar between both slices of bread and dip in egg wash. 
4. Pan fry in butter until golden brown on both sides. Enjoy!
.
.

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
2 lowcarb tortillas 
1 lb ground beef
1 cup marinara sauce
1 cup shredded mozarella
16 oz ricotta
1 cup grated parmesan
1 egg
1.5 tbsp oil
Seasonings of choice.
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cook ground beef, when finished, add marinara and switch heat to simmer until warm. Set aside.
2. Mix seasonings, ricotta, half of the Parmesan, and an egg in a bowl. Set aside.
3. In non stick or parchment lined baking dish add the meat sauce, tortilla, ricotta, meat sauce, mozzarella, parmesan & repeat .
4. Air fry at 400F for 10-12 mins. Slice into 4 squares. Enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

.
.
.
My lease ends tomorrow so I’m moving out of my apartment and into @anafioreo ‘s until our house is ready in March! The lives will continue tomorrow night at 8:30 PM EST in a new kitchen 🙌
.
.
Thank you to everyone who was a part of these livestreams over the past 14 months! I made some of the best memories of my life with you guys! I’m living my dream life and have the best job ever because of your support! #TurtleGang FOR LIFE !!! 🐢❤️
.
.

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
Boneless skinless chicken breasts
Crushed up pork rinds 
Large egg
EVOO
Salt
Pepper
Garlic powder
Fillings of your choice (we used spinach artichoke dip & green goddess Gouda)
.
.
Instructions:
1. Beat chicken breast until flat. Drizzle with EVOO. Season with salt, pepper, & garlic powder. 
2. Stuff with ingredients of your choice and close with tooth picks.
3. Coat in egg and crushed up pork rinds.
4. Air fry at 375F for 20 mins flipping halfway through. (Until internal temp reaches 165°F)
.
.
#keto #lowcarb

node.text:

.
Ingredients:
1 cup shredded mozzarella 
1/2 cup almond flour
2 tbsp cream cheese
1 egg
2 tsp garlic powder
1 tsp onion powder
1 tsp oregano 
1 tsp baking powder
Salt & pepper
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mix dry ingredients and set aside.
2. Mix cream cheese and mozzarella. Microwave for 1 minute.
3. Stir and microwave for 30 more seconds. Stir again. Add your whisked egg & dry ingredients. Mix. 
4. Knead and flatten out between two sheets of greased parchment paper. 
5. Cut out 2 inch wide strips, fold like a hot dog twice, roll them into a rope, & tie into a knot.
6. Air fry at 350F for 10 mins. (If you stuff them use parchment paper)
7. Brush with melted butter & garlic. Enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

Although it tasted REALLY good this recipe was kind of a fail because it didn’t hold together that well. So here is the chicken crust pizza recipe I typically use!
.
.
Ingredients: 
1 lb ground chicken
1/2 cup shredded mozarella
Seasonings of choice
Toppings of choice
.
.
. 
1. Preheat oven to 400F. Mix chicken, mozzarella, & seasonings together.
2. Shape into 1/2 inch thicc circle on a parchment lined baking sheet.
3. Bake for 17 minutes.
4. Take out, add toppings, and put back in for 10 minutes or until cheese melts. You can switch to broil for the last 2-3 minutes!
5. Enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

.
.
.
Ingredients:
Sirloin steak 
Worcestershire sauce
Avocado oil
Butter
Minced garlic
Seasonings of your choice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cut steak into cubes. Mix in a bowl with Worcestershire sauce, oil, & seasonings.
2. Air fry at 400F for 7 minutes.
3. In a bowl melt butter and garlic. Toss the finished steak in the bowl and enjoy!
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #steak #carnivore

.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 can of chicken
1 large egg
1/2 cup shredded cheese
Seasonings of choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mash your chicken up in a bowl and mix with all ingredients. 
2. Shape into nuggets and air fry on parchment paper at 400F for 8-10 minutes flipping halfway through.
3. Let cool & enjoy!
.
.
Notes: You can also bake at 400F for 20 mins flipping halfway.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
Say “YES” if you would eat this sausage and cabbage alfredo 😋🙌

1 head cabbage 
1.5 lbs smoked sausage
1.5 cup heavy cream 
6 oz cream cheese
3/4 cup butter
1 tbsp garlic
Parmesan 
Salt & pepper

1. In a baking dish combine all ingredients except sausage and parmesan. (This works best in a cast iron skillet)
2. Cover and bake at 400F for 30 minutes.
3. Brown sausage and set aside.
4. Take out the baking dish, add the sausage and the rest of the parmesan, put back in for 5-10 minutes. 
5. Remove from oven, let cool, & enjoy!

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes #alfredo

Egg
Butter
.

.
.

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
2 lowcarb tortillas 
1 lb ground beef
1 cup marinara sauce
1 cup shredded mozarella
16 oz ricotta
1 cup grated parmesan
1 egg
1.5 tbsp oil
Seasonings of choice.
.
.
Instructions:
1. Cook ground beef, when finished, add marinara and switch heat to simmer until warm. Set aside.
2. Mix seasonings, ricotta, half of the Parmesan, and an egg in a bowl. Set aside.
3. In non stick or parchment lined baking dish add the meat sauce, tortilla, ricotta, meat sauce, mozzarella, parmesan & repeat .
4. Air fry at 400F for 10-12 mins. Slice into 4 squares. Enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes
